This frame concerns a Cognizer's certainty about the correctness of beliefs or expectations. It only includes uses where a Cognizer is expressed.
Lermontov was certain he would come to the party.

believe.v, certain.a, certainty.n, confidence.n, confident.a, convinced.a, doubtful.a, doubt.n, doubt.v, dubious.a, know.v, positive.a, skeptical.a, skepticism.n, skeptic.n, sure.a, trust.v, uncertain.a, uncertainty.n, unsure.a
